# Environment Variables

## Required Variables

### Database
```bash
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://username:password@localhost:5432/whoami_db"
```
PostgreSQL database connection string for Prisma ORM.

### Authentication (Clerk)
```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="pk_test_..."
CLERK_SECRET_KEY="sk_test_..."
```
Clerk authentication keys for user management.

### Optional: Clerk URLs (for custom domains)
```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL="/sign-in"
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL="/sign-up"
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_IN_URL="/"
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_UP_URL="/onboarding"
```

## Setup Instructions

1. Copy this file to `.env.local`:
   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env.local
   ```

2. Fill in your actual values for each variable

3. Never commit `.env.local` to version control
